@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tcijoe(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.exp((v2 + 0.99 + v0 + 0.78)))
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.abs(wp.exp(v2 + 0.59)))
    v2 = v1
    tmp = wp.cos(v0)
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.cos(tmp + 0.16)) * v0)
    v2 = ((tmp - wp.abs(v0 + 0.11)) - ((v1 + 0.64 * v1 + 0.30) + (v1 + 0.29 + v0 + 0.07)))
    data[tid] = v0
